title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return recognizable strings
OB: Currently, when retrieving labels before extraction, the returned values are null. However, after extraction, recognizable strings are returned.
EB: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return recognizable strings. Since the labels need to be displayed to the end user before extraction, the getcolumnlabel method should return the same labels as after extraction.
